{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/4533","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/4533/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/4533/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/4533/events","html_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/4533","id":4210385885,"node_id":"PR_kwDOLW-eZs7QJRUk","number":4533,"title":"[toast] Add focus option to move focus to toast on open","user":{"login":"Jihye2ee","id":15521676,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE1NTIxNjc2","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/15521676?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee","html_url":"https://github.com/Jihye2ee","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Jihye2ee/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":6619776173,"node_id":"LA_kwDOLW-eZs8AAAABipHErQ","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/labels/PR:%20out-of-date","name":"PR: out-of-date","color":"ff9933","default":false,"description":"The pull request has merge conflicts and can't be merged."},{"id":6621343548,"node_id":"LA_kwDOLW-eZs8AAAABiqmvPA","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/labels/component:%20toast","name":"component: toast","color":"ffffff","default":false,"description":"Changes related to the toast component."}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":4,"created_at":"2026-04-06T07:52:25Z","updated_at":"2026-06-04T19:06:10Z","closed_at":"2026-06-04T19:06:09Z","assignee":null,"author_association":"NONE","issue_field_values":[],"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/pulls/4533","html_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/4533","diff_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/4533.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/mui/base-ui/pull/4533.patch","merged_at":null},"body":"## Summary\r\n\r\nAdds a `focus` option to `toastManager.add()` that moves focus to the toast when it opens. This enables keyboard and screen reader users to reach interactive actions (e.g. Undo) without relying on the F6 shortcut.\r\n\r\nCloses #4253\r\n\r\n## Changes\r\n\r\n- **`useToastManager.ts`** — Add `focus?: boolean` to `ToastObject`\r\n- **`ToastRoot.tsx`** — On mount, if `focus` is `true`: save `prevFocusElement`, focus the toast, pause timers, and set `focused` state (same pattern as F6 in `ToastViewport`)\r\n- **`ToastRoot.test.tsx`** — Add tests for focus behavior\r\n- **Undo demo** — Apply `focus: true` to demonstrate the pattern\r\n\r\n## How it works\r\n\r\n```\r\n1. toastManager.add({ focus: true, ... })\r\n2. Toast mounts → useEffect saves prevFocusElement, focuses the toast\r\n3. Viewport's handleFocus pauses timers (existing infra)\r\n4. User interacts (Undo/Close) or tabs away → timers resume (existing infra)\r\n5. On close → handleFocusManagement restores focus (existing infra)\r\n```\r\n\r\nWhen `focus` is not set, behavior is identical to before — no breaking changes.\r\n\r\n## Screenshot\r\n| Tab → Undo → Click | Tab → Undo → Tab out → auto-dismiss |\r\n|:---:|:---:|\r\n| <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/6bb401a0-099a-44e8-bbdc-c72127774430\" /> | <img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f11a8bef-b223-44c9-bf6c-e258556c99a5\" /> |\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"aarongarciah","id":7225802,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjcyMjU4MDI=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7225802?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah","html_url":"https://github.com/aarongarciah","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/aarongarciah/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/4533/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/mui/base-ui/issues/4533/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}